! Horizontal Story River

This plugin is an attempt to bring [[Andy Matuschak's Evergreen notes|https://notes.andymatuschak.org/]] system into [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com/]] that I found after reading articles by [[Anne-Laure Le Cunff|https://nesslabs.com/]].

Thanks both for the inspiration, my (thinking about) notes finally started to become (somehow) useful!

